<note n="556-1"/>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīsvasti namaḥstuṁga śiraścuṁbita caṁdracāmara cāravē trailōkya nagarāraṁbha mūlastaṁbhāya śaṁbhavē
<lb n="2"/>svastiśrī vijayādbhudaya <hi rend="bold">śālivāhana ṣakavaruṣa 1493 saṁduvartamāna prajōtpatya saṁvatsarada ve<note n="556-2"/> śudha 5 ravivāradallu</hi> śrīma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tu viṭhalada kuñi dēvarasarāda doṁbahegaḍeyaru tamage puṁṇyavāga bēkeṁdu gō <unclear>U</unclear> gaḷu Udakavakoṁba <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ḍisi hākidakallu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>giyanu tegadukoṁḍu hōdavarige kāśiyali sāvira kapileyaṁ koṁda pāpaveṁdu baradasāsanāṁkita <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> śubhamastu
</p>

